<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5e6d3; /* Light beige brown */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .error-container {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(93, 64, 55, 0.15);
            max-width: 480px;
            width: 100%;
        }

        .error-container img {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 260px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #5d4037; /* Dark brown */
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #8d6e63; /* Medium brown */
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #a1887f; /* Soft brown button */
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 30px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            background-color: #6d4c41; /* Darker brown on hover */
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/thumbnails/008/568/878/small_2x/website-page-not-found-error-404-oops-worried-robot-character-peeking-out-of-outer-space-site-crash-on-technical-work-web-design-template-with-chatbot-mascot-cartoon-online-bot-assistance-failure-vector.jpg" alt="404 Error">
        <h1>Oops! Page Not Found</h1>
        <p>Looks like the page you are trying to visit doesn’t exist.<br>Let’s get you back on track.</p>
        <a href="/">Go Back to Home</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
